or which the large black hole, quantum hot\nflat space, or both are the ground state. The corresponding phase diagram is\ndisplayed. Using the density of states $\\nu$ at a given energy $E$ we also find\nthat the entropy of the large black hole $r_{+2}$. In addition, we make the\nconnection between the five-dimensional thermodynamics and York's\nfour-dimensional results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-01"}
