operties of planet scattering remnants are strongly affected due to the\nchange in the branching ratio. We also find that the merger products have broad\ndistributions of spin magnitudes and obliquities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 18:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-16"}
