 Fibonacci\ndriving CFT can be mapped to the energy spectrum of electrons propagating in a\nFibonacci quasi-crystal. In addition, another quasi-periodically driven CFT\nwith an Aubry-Andr\\'e like sequence is also studied. We compare the CFT results\nto lattice calculations and find remarkable agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 18:00:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 15:03:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 14:37:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-19"}
