 temperature dependencies\nof the characteristic relaxation times and amplitudes of optical densities. At\nhighest fluences we observe electronic melting of the CDW and disappearance of\nthe mode hardening below T$_{CDW}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 00:12:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-30"}
