 that fast CMEs\noccuring in clusters tend to produce larger geomagnetic storms than isolated\nfast CMEs. This may be related to CME-CME interaction producing a more complex\nand stronger interaction with the Earth magnetosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 10:07:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Jun 2020 08:18:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-09"}
