g energy at low temperatures.\nConsideration and further exploration of these effects will be crucial when\nengineering skyrmion materials towards future applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 12:18:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-23"}
